    Verse: 8
Tags:
  - Possessions
---
Attachment to material things is a sign of inferiority, because the more a
man cares for the things of this world, the less does he understand his
destiny; his disinterestedness, on the contrary, proves that he has arrived
at a wider and clearer view of the future.
